text: Food stalls not that many. Alot of stalls are vacant. Food wise still ok to eat.
Yummy delicious vegetarian food found here...can't go wrong even for non-veg eater.
Non air conditioning food court. Busy during normal working days during lunch hour. Offers 1 malay and Indian food stall besides others. Reasonable prices.

Packed to the brim with customers. Place was clean and neat.

Had the Tanglin Halt Ban Mian for lunch. Not bad! Unique taste.
One of its kind food court to can eat and go will be smaller if compared to other but have good options and food is nice and have parking space beside
